                    <comment id="12908455" author="rcmuir" created="Sun, 12 Sep 2010 13:39:45 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;here&apos;s an initial patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i tried to fix some worst-case problems with similar tests as well, but some&lt;br/&gt;
